Class AfterParseOptions.AfterParseActions

java.lang.Object
lanat.AfterParseOptions.AfterParseActions
Enclosing class:
AfterParseOptions
public final class AfterParseOptions.AfterParseActions extends Object
Provides actions to be executed after parsing is done.

This class cannot be instantiated directly. Use AfterParseOptions.withActions(Consumer) to set the actions to be executed after parsing is done.
